    "title": "Innovation Program Manager",
    "excerpt": "<p>The Office of Data &amp; Innovation (ODI) is seeking an Innovation Program Manager. You will serve as a member of the Governmental Affairs and Innovation Training team and will manage the operations, strategy, and delivery of CalAcademy, and several strategic programs such as the Governor’s Innovation Fellows, the Innovation Labs, and Engaged California. Location: The &#8230; <a title=\"Innovation Program Manager\" class=\"read-more\" href=\"https://live-digital-ca-gov.pantheonsite.io/join-us/innovation-program-manager/\" aria-label=\"More on Innovation Program Manager\">Read more</a></p>\n",
